import * as React from "react"
import {
  ChakraProvider,
  CSSReset,
  Box,
  Grid,
  GridItem
} from "@chakra-ui/core"
import theme from "@chakra-ui/theme"

import { Header } from './components/Header';

export const App = () => (
  <ChakraProvider theme={theme}>
    <CSSReset />
    <Box textAlign="center" fontSize="md" bg="f6f6f6">
      <Header />
      <Grid templateRows="maxmin(200px, 1fr) auto">
        <GridItem bg="tomato" />
        <GridItem bg="yellow" />
      </Grid>
    </Box>
  </ChakraProvider>
)
